<p>We hope your trial of Tx Xchange is going well. At this point, there are a couple of activities we’d like to suggest you do to ensure you and your patients/clients are beginning to use the software.</p>
<ul>
  <li><b>Have you started to create patient/client records so you can begin to use Tx Xchange with them? It’s so easy – all you need is their name and email address.</b>To view how to Create a New Patient/Client Record, click <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/TxXchange#p/u" target="_blank">Support & Training Videos </a>.<br><br></li>
  <li><b>Have you taken a little time to create 10 template plans for your library? If so, you can quickly give your patients/clients personalized video-based plans and health literacy information with in less than 10 seconds. </b>Don’t remember how to? Click <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/TxXchange#p/u" target="_blank">Support & Training Videos </a>. You’ll find easy to follow videos that will demonstrate how to Create a Template Plan or Assign a Template Plan to your patient/client.<br><br></li>
  <li>If you haven’t signed up yet for our <a href=" http://www.txxchange.com/index.php/webinars/65" target="_blank">Getting Started with Tx Xchange </a> webinar, it’d be a great idea to do so. In just an hour, you’ll get trained on key features, the best next steps to take, and start successfully using the software with your patients or clients (you’re going to like their feedback!)<br><br></li>
  <li><b>Are you ready to start experiencing all the benefits of Tx Xchange? </b> If so, call or email us and we’ll convert your account from trial to full customer status. We’ll also get you signed up for our live webinar – <a href="http://www.txxchange.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=66&Itemid=13" target="_blank">Tx Xchange Best Practices</a> . We’ll demonstrate and discuss how current Tx Xchange customers use the software to achieve the business, health, and service oriented results they want To review our simple, no contract pricing, click <a href="http://www.txxchange.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=48&Itemid=12" target="_blank">here</a><br><br></li>
  <li>If you have any questions for us, please email <a href="mailto:support@txxchange.com">support@txxchange.com</a>or call 800-928-5351. We’ll do our best to get you the information you need to start experiencing all the benefits Tx Xchange has to offer your health, wellness, or fitness business.<br><br></li>
</ul>
